{"tid":1692723,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"髮型師店外被捕 警：唔代表唔係曱甴","createTime":"2019-11-04T08:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T08:33:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"815ae506f07a15ee7a30313d4061a6aeb0cc6edd","tid":1692723,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:18:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191104/AHJ7M3UJ2HLEWTLVNNPRTUE25U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191104%2FAHJ7M3UJ2HLEWTLVNNPRTUE25U%2F&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfnQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=b3c1d0bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191104%2FAHJ7M3UJ2HLEWTLVNNPRTUE25U%2F&h=bcc35f1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191104/AHJ7M3UJ2HLEWTLVNNPRTUE25U/</a><br />\n<br />\n髮型師店外被捕 警：唔代表唔係曱甴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/R73aqQ4sYMApGAmDPS8iDUMePwE=/802x333/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/I23RTQWIR5IB6GFNH5POUFHBMU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FR73aqQ4sYMApGAmDPS8iDUMePwE%3D%2F802x333%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FI23RTQWIR5IB6GFNH5POUFHBMU.gif&h=80a84f17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一間髮型屋的髮型師前日在午飯時間被捕（左圖），其同事嘗試與防暴警解釋不果（右圖）。讀者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】前日防暴警在多區大搜捕，當日下午4時，位於灣仔的Barber Shop髮型屋一名髮型師，在店外被多名防暴警拘捕，髮型屋同事跟警方理論，澄清被捕同事是在店內工作，但防暴警說：「喺度做嘢唔代表唔係曱甴！」過程被網民拍片上載社交網。<br />\n<br />\n髮型屋老闆是組合「廿四味」成員李凱賢（Brian），前晚髮型屋在社交網發出英文聲明：「今天（前日）我們經歷了非常不幸的遭遇，我們其中一位正在值班並從午休時間回來的理髮師被誤認了，在沒有明顯原因的情況下在灣仔被捕。即使同事趕緊出來確認他只是在工作，也無法為他辯護。我們將盡可能以任何方式提供法律支援幫助他，並希望他盡快返來，謝謝大家關心。」<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》昨日致電李凱賢了解，問到是否有髮型屋員工被捕，李在電話表示：「佢OK啦，冇事，佢出返嚟，有啲誤會啫，出面咁亂，多謝你關心。今朝出咗嚟。叫佢休息吓先，聽日先開工，都要瞓覺。」對於員工無辜被捕，李說：「我唔會mention（提及）呢啲嘢。」"},{"pid":"73727377cc50870eb949389704d825b5414e17af","tid":1692723,"uid":175159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:33:31.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n白宮聯署：制裁中共喉舌TVB，尚欠55,973個簽名，11月9日截止<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1692678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1692678</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}